text: Novy Ural () is a rural locality (a village) in Kukkuyanovsky Selsoviet, Dyurtyulinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 28 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 33 km from Dyurtyuli, 8 km from Kukkuyanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Dyurtyulinsky District
title: Novy Ural
